00:57:28.380 --> 00:57:31.480
As a seed when you plant it in

00:57:31.480 --> 00:57:35.040
the Mother Earth, the Mother Earth itself sprouts

00:57:35.040 --> 00:57:38.760
the seed spontaneously in the same way the

00:57:38.760 --> 00:57:39.900
Kundalini rises

00:57:39.900 --> 00:57:51.500
and

00:57:51.500 --> 00:57:53.180
gives you that power.

00:57:53.180 --> 00:57:57.720
By which you become collectively conscious.

00:58:03.520 --> 00:58:06.580
You can know about yourself and you can

00:58:06.580 --> 00:58:07.560
know about others.

00:58:13.020 --> 00:58:16.440
First of all your health improves, your diseases

00:58:16.440 --> 00:58:17.060
disappear.

00:58:22.580 --> 00:58:25.580
Sahaja Yoga had cured one person suffering from

00:58:25.580 --> 00:58:28.000
AIDS and he was quite alright for a

00:58:28.000 --> 00:58:29.940
year or so but again he went back

00:58:29.940 --> 00:58:31.880
to his bad habits and did not take

00:58:31.880 --> 00:58:38.500
to Sahaja Yoga and again he is sick.

00:58:51.660 --> 00:58:55.380
After all the Creator has created us with

00:58:55.380 --> 00:59:04.020
such care and love and there must be

00:59:04.020 --> 00:59:05.680
some purpose behind it.

00:59:11.520 --> 00:59:13.500
He doesn't want us to just end up

00:59:13.500 --> 00:59:16.180
as sex points or some sensational nonsense.

00:59:26.460 --> 00:59:29.680
So we should say that the Divine itself

00:59:29.680 --> 00:59:32.520
is anxious that you all should get your

00:59:32.520 --> 00:59:35.320
realization because you have been seekers of ages.

00:59:47.380 --> 00:59:50.680
The Kundalini awakening takes place and you can

00:59:50.680 --> 00:59:52.480
feel the cool breeze on top of your

00:59:52.480 --> 00:59:55.420
head and first time you start feeling the

00:59:55.420 --> 00:59:59.240
all pervading power of God's love as cool

00:59:59.240 --> 00:59:59.600
breeze.

01:00:16.700 --> 01:00:20.480
Shankaracharya has described us as salilam, sali means

01:00:20.480 --> 01:00:22.240
cool and cool and cool.

01:00:29.580 --> 01:00:33.060
Buddha also has talked of only Self-Realization.

01:00:37.500 --> 01:00:39.140
He did not want to talk of God

01:00:39.140 --> 01:00:41.540
because when you start talking of God everybody

01:00:41.540 --> 01:00:43.260
thinks they have become God themselves.

01:00:50.800 --> 01:00:53.980
So to be practical he and Mahavira both

01:00:53.980 --> 01:00:56.800
of them said that first have your realization

01:00:56.800 --> 01:00:57.680
then we'll talk.

01:01:11.060 --> 01:01:13.660
So we have to have our Self-Realization

01:01:13.660 --> 01:01:14.120
first.

01:01:19.060 --> 01:01:21.060
You may say that we would like to

01:01:21.060 --> 01:01:24.180
know all the intricacies and all the mechanism

01:01:24.180 --> 01:01:26.100
how it works out.

01:01:39.780 --> 01:01:43.160
You will know it but as if you

01:01:43.160 --> 01:01:45.520
have to put the light in this hall

01:01:45.520 --> 01:01:48.320
you have to just switch on once which

01:01:48.320 --> 01:01:50.100
can work the whole thing, it's all built

01:01:50.100 --> 01:01:50.340
in.

01:02:04.800 --> 01:02:06.760
Why not have the light first and then

01:02:06.760 --> 01:02:08.500
we'll talk about it, there's lot of time.

01:02:16.320 --> 01:02:19.120
I think that's what it is, what we

01:02:19.120 --> 01:02:19.860
have to achieve.

01:02:26.880 --> 01:02:30.000
Today it has been an introduction to Sahaja

01:02:30.000 --> 01:02:34.480
Yoga but tomorrow I'll elaborately tell, day after

01:02:34.480 --> 01:02:37.940
tomorrow isn't it, I'll elaborately tell you about

01:02:37.940 --> 01:02:44.120
what works it out, what is Kundalini, every

01:02:44.120 --> 01:02:46.720
details that we can touch in that short

01:02:46.720 --> 01:02:47.080
lecture.

01:02:47.080 --> 01:02:48.360
Thank you very much.

01:03:16.140 --> 01:03:18.340
But if you have any questions I will

01:03:18.340 --> 01:03:18.440
be happy to answer them.

01:03:27.140 --> 01:03:34.760
And then we'll have the session of realization

01:03:34.760 --> 01:03:35.220
also.

01:03:37.140 --> 01:03:38.300
What is he saying?

01:03:45.180 --> 01:03:46.640
What are you, you are telling Me in

01:03:46.640 --> 01:03:47.320
French or what?

01:03:50.180 --> 01:03:50.820
What's that?

01:04:01.840 --> 01:04:02.440
That's it.

01:04:03.000 --> 01:04:04.560
That's what we are going to have.

01:04:04.560 --> 01:04:08.080
First of all the realization and then we

01:04:08.080 --> 01:04:08.960
have a center here.

01:04:09.820 --> 01:04:12.440
We have some people who have been doing

01:04:12.440 --> 01:04:13.840
Sahaja Yoga for quite some time.

01:04:14.620 --> 01:04:16.180
You have to join them.

01:04:17.420 --> 01:04:20.500
They will tell you one by one how

01:04:20.500 --> 01:04:22.320
you master yourself fully.

01:04:23.080 --> 01:04:26.600
First of course is the realization but how

01:04:26.600 --> 01:04:29.120
to keep it up, how to use it,

01:04:29.580 --> 01:04:31.540
how to work it out, how to be

01:04:31.540 --> 01:04:34.200
the master, that you have to pay little

01:04:34.200 --> 01:04:34.580
time.

01:04:36.580 --> 01:04:39.860
They, I'm told the first time that the

01:04:39.860 --> 01:04:43.160
French are charging little money for the bookkeeping

01:04:43.900 --> 01:04:45.900
and the paper and the tapes, a little

01:04:45.900 --> 01:04:46.800
bit, not much.

01:04:47.100 --> 01:04:49.040
Of course I don't take any money and

01:04:49.040 --> 01:04:50.180
you cannot purchase Me.

01:04:50.560 --> 01:04:51.640
It cannot be purchased.

01:04:53.260 --> 01:04:56.680
So I, it's a very little money, that's

01:04:56.680 --> 01:04:58.420
what they said, that they have to charge

01:04:58.420 --> 01:05:01.420
because all the pressure of everything was on

01:05:01.420 --> 01:05:01.700
them.

01:05:02.000 --> 01:05:02.640
So it's all right.

01:05:02.740 --> 01:05:03.760
I mean they will show you all the

01:05:03.760 --> 01:05:05.340
accounts where they send spending.

01:06:24.880 --> 01:06:27.300
There is one more point I want to

01:06:27.300 --> 01:06:31.020
make it, that Freud has said that we

01:06:31.020 --> 01:06:32.820
should not be conditioned by anything.

01:06:32.820 --> 01:06:36.960
So our egos have developed too much.

01:06:54.960 --> 01:06:57.860
And we say, what's wrong in everything we

01:06:57.860 --> 01:06:58.120
do?

01:07:04.600 --> 01:07:07.480
Like in England some people came to Me

01:07:07.480 --> 01:07:12.960
with painted hair and funny dresses and I

01:07:12.960 --> 01:07:14.200
asked them, why do you do it?

01:07:14.260 --> 01:07:15.080
They said, what's wrong?

01:07:25.380 --> 01:07:28.720
I said, it's wrong because your eyesight will

01:07:28.720 --> 01:07:29.320
become weak.

01:07:40.060 --> 01:07:45.780
But if we do not understand the practical

01:07:45.780 --> 01:07:49.500
way of life which is balance, we really

01:07:49.500 --> 01:07:50.820
become very one-sided.

01:08:04.060 --> 01:08:06.360
So now we have to understand that it

01:08:06.360 --> 01:08:07.680
is not a mental projection.

01:08:13.860 --> 01:08:16.500
And when the triggering of the Kundalini takes

01:08:16.500 --> 01:08:20.640
place, actually it presses on both the sides

01:08:20.640 --> 01:08:22.960
or sucks in on both the sides the

01:08:22.960 --> 01:08:24.760
ego and the superego as you see there,

01:08:25.399 --> 01:08:27.359
the conditioning as well as your ego.

01:08:43.880 --> 01:08:46.240
And this portion of the head, which is

01:08:46.240 --> 01:08:48.479
the fontanel bone area, becomes softer.

01:08:55.080 --> 01:08:56.720
Actually it happens.

01:09:00.859 --> 01:09:04.979
Then you do not get conditioned nor into

01:09:04.979 --> 01:09:08.100
ego but you become the Spirit, the free

01:09:08.100 --> 01:09:08.620
Spirit.

01:09:19.040 --> 01:09:20.939
The Spirit of Wisdom.

01:09:23.200 --> 01:09:26.460
You start feeling the vibrations of cool breeze

01:09:26.460 --> 01:09:35.800
on your hands, fingertips, and you start

01:09:36.800 --> 01:09:40.500
and you can find out fundamental answers to

01:09:40.500 --> 01:09:41.460
any questions.

01:09:46.420 --> 01:09:50.300
As if you become a complete computer.

01:09:54.580 --> 01:10:00.220
First time the Absolute starts asserting itself, manifesting

01:10:00.220 --> 01:10:11.620
itself on the central nervous system.

01:10:15.280 --> 01:10:19.280
So whatever you feel on your central nervous

01:10:19.280 --> 01:10:21.240
system is the evolutionary gain.

01:10:31.939 --> 01:10:33.719
That is a real ascent, not just a

01:10:39.626 --> 01:10:41.873
mental projection,

01:10:44.573 --> 01:10:49.646
not some sort of a subservient attitude towards someone

01:10:53.313 --> 01:11:00.760
 or accepting somebody because he appeals to your mind.

01:11:04.880 --> 01:11:09.680
But you become the absolute discriminating element, that

01:11:09.680 --> 01:11:10.340
is the Spirit.

01:11:19.573 --> 01:11:24.800
Element, you become the element of that.

01:11:30.086 --> 01:11:34.140
So we have to understand that we have

01:11:34.140 --> 01:11:37.020
such a potential within us.

01:11:41.440 --> 01:11:44.120
Like a television, if you see it looks

01:11:44.120 --> 01:11:46.600
like a box, but when you put to

01:11:46.600 --> 01:11:48.820
the mains, you know what it is.

01:11:58.760 --> 01:12:02.280
In the same way this human being that

01:12:02.280 --> 01:12:05.060
looks very ordinary is tremendous.

01:12:12.800 --> 01:12:14.100
It is fantastic.

01:12:15.320 --> 01:12:17.300
Only it is to be put to the

01:12:17.300 --> 01:12:22.560
mains and the connections have to be fixed

01:12:22.560 --> 01:12:23.180
properly.

01:12:29.540 --> 01:12:31.220
It can be sometimes loose.

01:12:34.480 --> 01:12:36.840
Only that alertness is needed.

01:12:43.140 --> 01:12:45.140
Sahaja also means easy.

01:12:48.880 --> 01:12:51.180
Whatever is spontaneous is the easiest.

01:12:55.700 --> 01:12:57.940
Whatever is vital has to be easiest.

01:13:01.300 --> 01:13:03.260
Say for our breathing if you have to

01:13:03.260 --> 01:13:05.180
get to a guru, what will happen to

01:13:05.180 --> 01:13:05.500
us?

01:13:11.580 --> 01:13:12.720
That's what it is.

01:13:16.340 --> 01:13:17.260
Any other question?

01:13:23.313 --> 01:13:24.440
Yes

01:13:26.106 --> 01:13:28.833
From here, the lady

01:13:32.486 --> 01:13:34.053
What did she say ?

01:13:40.260 --> 01:13:44.080
Here only just now, just now, nowhere to

01:13:44.080 --> 01:13:46.140
go, here, all right.

01:13:46.140 --> 01:13:48.120
What else did you say, sir?

01:13:48.820 --> 01:13:52.540
Once you have this realization, can you fall

01:13:52.540 --> 01:13:55.080
back to sleep again and forget it?

01:13:55.320 --> 01:13:55.800
Can you?

01:13:56.380 --> 01:13:59.500
Fall back to sleep, fall asleep again.

01:14:00.480 --> 01:14:01.400
No, you shouldn't.

01:14:01.500 --> 01:14:02.160
Why do you sleep?

01:14:02.800 --> 01:14:04.100
You have to be alert.

01:14:04.860 --> 01:14:06.300
You have to work for God.

01:14:06.540 --> 01:14:08.180
You have to give realizations to others.

01:14:08.880 --> 01:14:09.740
You are now enlightened.

01:14:10.440 --> 01:14:12.780
As Christ has said, the light is not

01:14:12.780 --> 01:14:13.740
put under the table.

01:14:13.740 --> 01:14:15.120
Why should you sleep?

01:14:15.920 --> 01:14:17.440
We have to work very hard.

01:14:17.640 --> 01:14:19.220
We have to save thousands and thousands.

01:14:20.160 --> 01:14:23.680
The epidemic is coming of satanic forces like

01:14:23.680 --> 01:14:24.800
drugs, this, that.

01:14:25.080 --> 01:14:26.160
Who's going to work it out?

01:14:49.740 --> 01:14:54.120
By doing all this, you are relaxed.

01:14:58.220 --> 01:15:03.780
You do it as a drama, as a

01:15:03.780 --> 01:15:04.480
play, lila.

01:15:09.100 --> 01:15:09.860
What else?

01:15:09.940 --> 01:15:12.580
Did you ask some question there, gentleman, there?

01:15:16.020 --> 01:15:18.380
Yes, madame?

01:15:34.316 --> 01:15:35.102
You tell Me.

01:15:37.120 --> 01:15:38.680
Make it short, madame.

01:15:40.720 --> 01:15:41.900
What is it?

01:15:48.400 --> 01:15:50.220
What she said?

01:16:01.780 --> 01:16:04.500
There are very few.

01:16:04.700 --> 01:16:06.800
They are hiding in the Himalayas.

01:16:06.800 --> 01:16:08.520
They don't want to face.

01:16:08.940 --> 01:16:12.280
I sent one gentleman to America.

01:16:12.520 --> 01:16:14.520
He ran away from there in three days.

01:16:15.360 --> 01:16:16.060
He wouldn't stick on.

01:16:33.880 --> 01:16:35.420
But I'm not a guru.

01:16:35.420 --> 01:16:36.320
I'm a mother.

01:16:38.440 --> 01:16:39.740
And you have to become the guru.

01:16:40.020 --> 01:16:41.540
You have to become your own guru.

01:16:46.940 --> 01:16:49.320
You don't need any other guru but yourself.

01:16:53.790 --> 01:16:54.070
Good.

01:16:57.780 --> 01:16:58.660
All right, now.

01:16:58.980 --> 01:16:59.140
Yes?

01:17:01.800 --> 01:17:02.720
What did he say?

01:17:12.820 --> 01:17:14.540
Not at all, not at all.

01:17:14.740 --> 01:17:15.520
Who told you that?

01:17:15.900 --> 01:17:16.360
No, no, no.

01:17:16.460 --> 01:17:17.840
All that is all facts.

01:17:19.820 --> 01:17:22.660
You see, one should eat whatever is suitable

01:17:22.660 --> 01:17:23.380
to us.

01:17:23.820 --> 01:17:25.480
For example, I would say those who eat

01:17:25.480 --> 01:17:27.040
too much of cheese should not eat.

01:17:28.040 --> 01:17:29.000
That's French.

01:17:35.340 --> 01:17:36.040
Slaughtered what?

01:17:39.660 --> 01:17:41.380
So what is he worried about?

01:17:47.160 --> 01:17:49.420
Now, just see what I would suggest now.

01:17:49.840 --> 01:17:53.840
For people who are right-sided, they should

01:17:53.840 --> 01:17:54.860
not eat too much meat.

01:17:54.860 --> 01:17:57.040
But those who are left-sided should eat.

01:17:57.420 --> 01:17:58.940
Otherwise they'll be even worse.

01:17:59.960 --> 01:18:01.780
Left-sided people must eat meat.

01:18:02.360 --> 01:18:03.780
But now, just a minute, just a minute,

01:18:03.860 --> 01:18:04.240
just a minute.

01:18:04.660 --> 01:18:07.500
Now, by saving the chickens, what are we

01:18:07.500 --> 01:18:08.080
going to achieve?

01:18:08.820 --> 01:18:10.700
Chickens, am I going to give them realization?

01:18:11.980 --> 01:18:13.420
Can I give to the pigs?

01:18:13.700 --> 01:18:14.100
Can I?

01:18:15.200 --> 01:18:16.660
Save the human beings first.

01:18:17.040 --> 01:18:20.040
Please pay attention to the most important thing.

01:18:20.100 --> 01:18:20.900
They are human beings.

01:18:21.680 --> 01:18:23.340
There are people who need proteins.

01:18:23.340 --> 01:18:24.620
They have to have proteins.

01:18:24.720 --> 01:18:26.820
Like in India, I would say many people

01:18:26.820 --> 01:18:27.580
should have proteins.

01:18:27.680 --> 01:18:28.920
If they can afford, they should have.

01:18:29.260 --> 01:18:30.060
But they are very weak.

01:18:31.200 --> 01:18:33.340
Mentally they are all right, but muscular.

01:18:34.360 --> 01:18:36.140
You may not agree, but that's what it

01:18:36.140 --> 01:18:38.400
is, because if by becoming vegetarian, if you

01:18:38.400 --> 01:18:40.340
get to God and by starving and fasting,

01:18:40.640 --> 01:18:42.040
we are already doing it in India.

01:18:43.860 --> 01:18:45.540
If you want to have fasting, you'll have

01:18:45.540 --> 01:18:46.540
fasting all your lives.

01:18:47.040 --> 01:18:47.880
That's what it is.

01:18:49.060 --> 01:18:51.080
When the Jews did not believe in Christ,

01:18:51.080 --> 01:18:53.160
they said, we must have suffering, they had

01:18:53.160 --> 01:18:53.380
it.

01:18:53.860 --> 01:18:55.460
And now you ask for fasting, you'll have

01:18:55.460 --> 01:18:55.600
it.

01:18:55.880 --> 01:18:56.660
Lives together.

01:18:57.260 --> 01:18:57.880
Better starve.

01:18:58.540 --> 01:18:59.260
That's what you want.

01:19:00.060 --> 01:19:01.620
Do you want your spirit or you want

01:19:01.620 --> 01:19:02.360
all these things?

01:19:02.760 --> 01:19:04.240
By these things you are not going to

01:19:04.240 --> 01:19:04.760
reach to God.

01:19:04.880 --> 01:19:06.300
On the contrary, you must have a good

01:19:06.300 --> 01:19:06.600
health.

01:19:06.940 --> 01:19:08.580
If you don't have a good health, you

01:19:08.580 --> 01:19:09.840
cannot be a good Sahaja Yogi.

01:19:10.940 --> 01:19:12.540
But all the yogis are vegetarians.

01:19:12.640 --> 01:19:14.020
They would never touch meat, I know.

01:19:14.080 --> 01:19:15.700
Who is a, you tell Me one name.

01:19:16.140 --> 01:19:17.560
You just tell Me one, who is a

01:19:17.560 --> 01:19:19.000
other yogi according to you.

01:19:19.020 --> 01:19:19.900
What good they have done.

01:19:19.900 --> 01:19:20.960
Have they given Realization?

01:19:21.120 --> 01:19:22.200
You are not realized yourself.

01:19:22.760 --> 01:19:23.860
If you have met them, why didn't you

01:19:23.860 --> 01:19:24.620
get your Realization?

01:19:25.600 --> 01:19:26.640
Why are you getting angry?

01:19:26.900 --> 01:19:27.940
No, I'm not getting angry.

01:19:28.020 --> 01:19:29.660
I'm just asking you, you, if I'm not

01:19:29.660 --> 01:19:30.100
getting angry.

01:19:30.160 --> 01:19:32.020
What makes you think I'm getting angry?

01:19:32.740 --> 01:19:34.580
I'm on the loudspeaker, you are not, that's

01:19:34.580 --> 01:19:34.740
all.

01:19:37.840 --> 01:19:38.340
All right?

01:19:38.720 --> 01:19:39.500
This is not the way.

01:19:39.680 --> 01:19:41.740
You see, we must understand what have we

01:19:41.740 --> 01:19:42.880
been doing so far.

01:19:43.400 --> 01:19:44.940
What did we achieve out of it?

01:19:45.000 --> 01:19:45.660
Be sensible.

01:19:46.000 --> 01:19:46.880
You have to be sensible.

01:19:46.880 --> 01:19:50.020
And the sense is that if you go

01:19:50.020 --> 01:19:53.000
on paying attention to things which are not

01:19:53.000 --> 01:19:57.260
concerning the Spirit, it won't work out.

01:19:57.880 --> 01:20:00.820
Like Krishna killed many people, He had to.

01:20:01.780 --> 01:20:03.860
The Goddess had to kill so many rakshasas

01:20:03.860 --> 01:20:04.900
and devils, She had to.

01:20:05.680 --> 01:20:08.840
She had to even drink the blood of

01:20:08.840 --> 01:20:09.700
this Rakta Bija.

01:20:10.420 --> 01:20:11.760
If you have read the books, you will

01:20:11.760 --> 01:20:13.060
know what they had to do.

01:20:13.060 --> 01:20:16.740
After all, you see, whatever has to be

01:20:16.740 --> 01:20:17.620
done, has to be done.

01:20:22.880 --> 01:20:24.280
That's all right.

01:20:26.140 --> 01:20:26.940
No, no.

01:20:27.860 --> 01:20:29.440
All right, let's have it.

01:20:29.900 --> 01:20:32.460
You see, you must have more care for

01:20:32.460 --> 01:20:35.660
the human beings, not for all these things.

01:20:35.800 --> 01:20:38.420
You see, there is a community in India

01:20:38.420 --> 01:20:39.180
called Jains.

01:20:39.180 --> 01:20:41.740
They even try to save the bugs and

01:20:41.740 --> 01:20:42.300
the mosquitoes.

01:20:43.600 --> 01:20:45.820
Are we going to give Realization to mosquitoes?

01:20:50.780 --> 01:20:53.880
He never said it.

01:20:54.360 --> 01:20:56.560
Now, about Buddha, don't tell Me, because Buddha

01:20:56.560 --> 01:20:59.160
died by eating the pig.

01:20:59.520 --> 01:21:01.080
Now, He could not have been said that.

01:21:01.900 --> 01:21:02.440
Is not true.

01:21:03.100 --> 01:21:03.460
All right?

01:21:04.360 --> 01:21:05.060
That settles it.

01:21:06.040 --> 01:21:08.180
Buddha, don't try to manipulate.

01:21:08.180 --> 01:21:10.480
He has been very much manipulated.

01:21:11.520 --> 01:21:13.720
When I went to China, luckily because of

01:21:13.720 --> 01:21:16.080
My husband I travel a lot, I was

01:21:16.080 --> 01:21:20.400
surprised the lama, the Dalai Lama, his things

01:21:20.400 --> 01:21:23.180
were kept there, written in Pali, because I

01:21:23.180 --> 01:21:24.160
read Pali.

01:21:24.960 --> 01:21:27.320
And all the things that he had were

01:21:27.320 --> 01:21:29.100
made of solid gold.

01:21:29.920 --> 01:21:33.240
His beer cup, his another jug, they stacked.

01:21:33.340 --> 01:21:35.340
He's a vegetarian for every purpose.

01:21:35.340 --> 01:21:39.560
But all the money, all the money that

01:21:39.560 --> 01:21:42.640
he got it from these poor Tibetans, and

01:21:42.640 --> 01:21:44.440
even today if you go and see him,

01:21:44.780 --> 01:21:46.680
he is the one who is introducing drugs.

01:21:47.580 --> 01:21:48.840
Nobody understands you, Mother.

01:21:49.000 --> 01:21:50.400
You should leave now to translate.

01:21:50.420 --> 01:21:51.180
All right, all right.

01:21:51.300 --> 01:21:51.960
He understands.

01:21:52.200 --> 01:21:53.240
He understands.

01:21:53.460 --> 01:21:53.560
Yeah.

01:24:10.160 --> 01:24:12.780
And this is a very good example, of

01:24:12.780 --> 01:24:15.920
showing how a person who is kind to

01:24:15.920 --> 01:24:19.180
the animals like Dalai Lama and to the

01:24:19.180 --> 01:24:24.720
poor Tibetans, he actually sucked their blood, because

01:24:24.720 --> 01:24:26.480
I don't know how he made so much

01:24:26.480 --> 01:24:29.240
gold, that he had plates of gold and

01:24:29.240 --> 01:24:29.500
everything.

01:24:29.680 --> 01:24:31.300
And even if you go and see him

01:24:31.300 --> 01:24:35.680
now in Dharamshala, he has a complete big

01:24:35.680 --> 01:24:38.840
Buddha made out of real gold and he

01:24:38.840 --> 01:24:41.300
takes food in nothing but gold.

01:24:41.460 --> 01:24:45.080
Even his bath tub, like what we call

01:24:45.080 --> 01:24:47.780
a Ganga in Indian language, that's not a

01:24:47.780 --> 01:24:49.780
tub, but a kind of a big bucket

01:24:49.780 --> 01:24:52.020
sort of a thing, was of real gold.

01:24:52.620 --> 01:24:55.000
I mean, imagine the compassion of this man.

01:24:56.000 --> 01:25:01.500
The Tibetans, poor things, suffering, without any warm

01:25:01.500 --> 01:25:05.280
clothes, very cold country, and this gentleman making

01:25:05.280 --> 01:25:07.280
all the gold for himself.

01:25:08.000 --> 01:25:09.040
What is the compassion?

01:25:09.200 --> 01:25:11.620
And we have many communities in India like

01:25:11.620 --> 01:25:15.380
that, who are absolute vegetarians and extremely cruel.

01:25:15.640 --> 01:25:17.800
All the Tibetans are not vegetarians, there's only

01:25:17.800 --> 01:25:19.640
the Dalai Lama who is, because all the

01:25:19.640 --> 01:25:20.920
Tibetans, they eat lots of meat.

01:25:21.480 --> 01:25:24.460
But he, I'm talking about Dalai Lama and

01:25:24.460 --> 01:25:25.180
his personal life.

01:25:25.220 --> 01:25:26.600
But I can tell you one thing about

01:25:26.600 --> 01:25:28.520
Dalai Lama, I was in Germany when he

01:25:28.520 --> 01:25:30.220
gave his speech, and in this half an

01:25:30.220 --> 01:25:33.020
hour, he was talking about twenty times, one

01:25:33.020 --> 01:25:34.540
word, you know what it was, it was

01:25:34.540 --> 01:25:35.620
warm, hot meat.

01:25:36.260 --> 01:25:36.760
He talks.

01:25:37.600 --> 01:25:39.320
Talking is different, doing is different.

01:25:39.560 --> 01:25:41.620
What is wrong with his speech?

01:25:42.940 --> 01:25:44.640
Now you go to him, that's the best

01:25:44.640 --> 01:25:46.040
for you, and then when you are hurt,

01:25:46.140 --> 01:25:47.540
don't come to me, that's all.

01:25:48.000 --> 01:25:49.980
I just said, Buddha said also, I didn't

01:25:49.980 --> 01:25:50.120
say anything.

01:25:50.120 --> 01:25:51.960
No, no, no, you don't know, just now

01:25:51.960 --> 01:25:54.340
I've told you that Buddha used to eat

01:25:54.340 --> 01:25:55.260
meat, it's proved.

01:25:55.840 --> 01:25:58.560
So you don't now try to establish something

01:25:58.560 --> 01:26:00.560
and spoil everybody's chances of Realization.

01:26:00.680 --> 01:26:02.400
If you don't want, you can go, but

01:26:02.400 --> 01:26:03.220
don't trouble others.

01:26:03.320 --> 01:26:04.460
You see, this is not the way to

01:26:04.460 --> 01:26:05.820
discuss, it's going too far.

01:26:06.140 --> 01:26:07.980
All right, now I've given you time, please.

01:26:08.340 --> 01:26:09.580
Now, any other question?

01:27:06.620 --> 01:27:07.740
All right.

01:27:08.100 --> 01:27:09.920
Now the thing is, one thing one must

01:27:09.920 --> 01:27:12.440
understand, that compassion doesn't talk.

01:27:13.740 --> 01:27:16.420
You don't have to talk, it acts, it

01:27:16.420 --> 01:27:16.820
works.

01:27:17.180 --> 01:27:19.580
It doesn't talk, it's silent.

01:27:20.560 --> 01:27:22.820
To see the compassion of a person, you

01:27:22.820 --> 01:27:23.580
should see Christ.

01:27:24.580 --> 01:27:28.860
Somebody touched the cloth of Christ and that

01:27:28.860 --> 01:27:29.380
was cured.

01:27:29.840 --> 01:27:31.620
And you must know, Sahaja Yoga has cured

01:27:31.620 --> 01:27:34.480
many people, just like that.

01:27:35.700 --> 01:27:37.900
People have given up their drugs just like

01:27:37.900 --> 01:27:38.280
that.

01:27:58.420 --> 01:28:02.586
The power of compassion is the power of God

01:28:06.639 --> 01:28:08.099
Which is the all-pervading power

01:28:11.293 --> 01:28:16.933
Which acts, which thinks, which understands, which corrects

01:28:20.099 --> 01:28:21.706
Which redeems

01:28:24.533 --> 01:28:26.733
which completely transforms you.

01:28:31.000 --> 01:28:32.660
That is what is compassion.

01:28:35.180 --> 01:28:36.780
You don't have to talk about it.

01:28:38.460 --> 01:28:40.460
You have to feel it, it is all pervading

01:28:52.760 --> 01:28:57.200
First, there are things, I follow your teaching

01:28:57.200 --> 01:29:00.540
very well, that is, be enlightened first, and

01:29:00.540 --> 01:29:02.780
then talk, I understand that.

01:29:03.240 --> 01:29:05.320
But unfortunately there are many people who are

01:29:05.320 --> 01:29:10.340
not enlightened, and then the questions I want

01:29:10.340 --> 01:29:12.040
to ask are the following ones.

01:29:12.420 --> 01:29:15.540
First you said, when you are enlightened, you

01:29:15.540 --> 01:29:17.020
do not have diseases.

01:29:17.466 --> 01:29:17.680
No.

01:29:17.760 --> 01:29:22.860
But I have many examples of Ramana Maharshi,

01:29:23.320 --> 01:29:24.420
who died of cancer.

01:29:25.720 --> 01:29:27.360
Who died of cancer?

01:29:27.960 --> 01:29:29.040
Ramana Maharshi.

01:29:29.120 --> 01:29:31.260
That was one mishap.

01:29:31.860 --> 01:29:34.600
I tell you why, because even if some

01:29:34.600 --> 01:29:36.640
are realized souls, I must say Ramana Maharshi

01:29:36.640 --> 01:29:38.280
was a great personality, no doubt.

01:29:39.880 --> 01:29:43.400
But the thing is, you see, some people

01:29:43.400 --> 01:29:48.480
died of cancer because they had no one

01:29:48.480 --> 01:29:50.180
to tell them how to get cured.

01:29:52.500 --> 01:29:53.780
I am here to tell you.

01:29:54.560 --> 01:29:55.820
I know how to do it.

01:29:56.640 --> 01:29:57.860
I know the trick.

01:29:58.840 --> 01:29:59.160
All right?

01:29:59.480 --> 01:30:00.240
This is the reason.

01:30:01.240 --> 01:30:02.840
I know he died, I am very sorry,

01:30:02.940 --> 01:30:04.500
because he was a realized soul, no doubt.

01:30:04.500 --> 01:30:06.060
He was a great person.

01:30:06.760 --> 01:30:08.440
But I was not there at that time.

01:30:09.600 --> 01:30:11.500
I can tell you how to cure cancer.

01:30:11.860 --> 01:30:15.660
I have cured the cancer of our ex

01:30:15.660 --> 01:30:19.900
president, who was Mr. Sanjeev Reddy.

01:30:20.280 --> 01:30:21.580
You may write to him and find out.

01:30:21.880 --> 01:30:22.640
In ten minutes.

01:30:32.600 --> 01:30:36.560
No, no, please stand up and say.

01:30:36.620 --> 01:30:37.580
We can't hear you.

01:30:37.940 --> 01:30:38.040
Just.

01:30:41.340 --> 01:30:42.300
All right.

01:30:46.140 --> 01:30:47.660
No, no, you say hello.

01:30:47.980 --> 01:30:48.360
See now.

01:30:48.780 --> 01:30:50.320
I will say in short one thing.

01:30:50.320 --> 01:30:50.760
Let us see.

01:30:50.820 --> 01:30:51.840
Whatever I have said it.

01:30:51.920 --> 01:30:52.900
See, see, hello.

01:30:53.140 --> 01:30:53.820
I'll just tell him.

01:30:54.020 --> 01:30:54.820
He understands English.

01:30:54.940 --> 01:30:55.520
I'll just tell him.

01:30:55.980 --> 01:30:57.020
Whatever I am saying.

01:30:57.380 --> 01:30:58.420
Hello, just a minute.

01:30:58.740 --> 01:30:59.360
Just a minute.

01:30:59.540 --> 01:31:00.020
Listen to me.

01:31:00.060 --> 01:31:00.540
One minute.

01:31:00.920 --> 01:31:01.840
No, no, let me tell him.

01:31:02.040 --> 01:31:03.600
Just don't confuse everyone.

01:31:04.460 --> 01:31:06.100
Whatever I am saying, it is to be

01:31:06.100 --> 01:31:08.060
first of all seen if it works or

01:31:08.060 --> 01:31:08.180
not.

01:31:08.280 --> 01:31:10.960
Supposing it is My hypothesis as a scientist,

01:31:11.340 --> 01:31:13.540
you must have patience, see for yourself it

01:31:13.540 --> 01:31:14.200
works or not.

01:31:14.680 --> 01:31:16.560
If it does not work, then you can

01:31:16.560 --> 01:31:18.200
say, but just now you have patience.

01:31:18.200 --> 01:31:20.580
You cannot just now by argument, how will

01:31:20.580 --> 01:31:21.080
I prove it?

01:31:21.620 --> 01:31:22.600
All right, sit down.

01:31:22.980 --> 01:31:24.960
So we better take the medicine and see.

01:31:28.180 --> 01:31:29.440
Now they want to have it.

01:31:29.560 --> 01:31:29.780
All right.

01:31:30.920 --> 01:31:32.160
We'll do one thing.

01:31:32.220 --> 01:31:33.740
You write it down your question, I'll answer

01:31:33.740 --> 01:31:34.040
tomorrow.

01:31:34.160 --> 01:31:36.020
They are very anxious to have Realization.

01:31:36.140 --> 01:31:36.320
Also.

01:31:41.046 --> 01:31:42.286
They are impatient.

01:31:57.740 --> 01:31:59.880
I think you should write down all your

01:31:59.880 --> 01:32:02.340
questions, leave it to Me tomorrow, and I'll

01:32:02.340 --> 01:32:03.020
try to answer.

01:32:03.320 --> 01:32:05.320
Because it's not difficult to answer this question.

01:32:06.440 --> 01:32:07.540
But can you wait?

01:32:07.680 --> 01:32:08.800
Why not have Realization?

01:32:09.060 --> 01:32:10.300
Just have Realization there.

01:32:10.420 --> 01:32:10.680
All right?

01:32:10.860 --> 01:32:11.640
Have patience.

01:32:12.060 --> 01:32:13.220
Let us have water, please.

01:32:21.180 --> 01:32:23.240
It's good that you can ask Me questions.

01:32:25.960 --> 01:32:29.380
But I like it that you can ask

01:32:29.380 --> 01:32:29.880
Me questions.

01:32:30.020 --> 01:32:32.140
I like it very much for one reason,

01:32:32.440 --> 01:32:33.640
that you are free.

01:32:34.240 --> 01:32:35.140
It shows you are free.

01:32:35.780 --> 01:32:37.140
You are not under any spell.

01:32:37.740 --> 01:32:39.760
It's a very good sign that you can

01:32:39.760 --> 01:32:40.500
ask Me questions.

01:32:40.840 --> 01:32:42.260
But those who have been to gurus, they

01:32:42.260 --> 01:32:42.980
never ask questions.

01:32:43.060 --> 01:32:44.120
They just go on paying money.

01:33:07.840 --> 01:33:11.520
So let us first get Realization, because the

01:33:11.520 --> 01:33:13.760
knowledge is very, very great.

01:33:13.760 --> 01:33:16.500
I must have given at least three thousand

01:33:16.500 --> 01:33:17.780
lectures in English language.

01:33:18.140 --> 01:33:18.640
At least.

01:33:19.460 --> 01:33:21.740
Now it's not, cannot be discussed in one

01:33:21.740 --> 01:33:22.020
lecture.

01:33:22.900 --> 01:33:25.600
Now there are majority of the people want

01:33:25.600 --> 01:33:26.100
Realization.

01:33:26.420 --> 01:33:28.060
So let us yield to the majority.

01:33:28.660 --> 01:33:29.000
All right?

01:33:30.973 --> 01:33:42.386
(Shri Mataji speaks Indian)

01:33:46.920 --> 01:33:48.580
people want Realization.

01:35:01.140 --> 01:35:02.040
Let's have it now.

01:35:03.406 --> 01:35:05.860
Anyway, I think the lady sitting next to

01:35:05.860 --> 01:35:06.720
you finds it difficult.

01:35:07.120 --> 01:35:09.300
Let her come in front, next to you.

01:35:09.680 --> 01:35:10.260
She could come.

01:35:10.560 --> 01:35:12.420
The lady next to you, this lady, there.

01:35:13.100 --> 01:35:13.900
The other side.

01:35:15.560 --> 01:35:17.940
Now the first thing is, you have to

01:35:17.940 --> 01:35:18.560
be comfortable.

01:35:20.286 --> 01:35:21.513
If there is

01:35:27.073 --> 01:35:29.340
because your attention should not be diverted.

01:35:30.020 --> 01:35:32.520
You have come for the first time, and

01:35:32.520 --> 01:35:35.240
attention can be diverted very easily.

01:35:44.250 --> 01:35:46.730
Because the attention is like, say, like My

01:35:46.730 --> 01:35:49.030
sari, you can say that, spread out, and

01:35:49.030 --> 01:35:50.890
the Kundalini pushes it in.

01:35:51.430 --> 01:35:53.510
So if it is tied outside, it's rather

01:35:53.510 --> 01:35:53.910
difficult.

01:36:13.556 --> 01:36:16.510
So the attention has to be kept free.

01:36:21.030 --> 01:36:23.910
Secondly, if you think anything is tight on

01:36:23.910 --> 01:36:27.450
your neck or on your waist, anywhere tight,

01:36:27.830 --> 01:36:29.830
just little bit reduce the pressures.

01:36:41.550 --> 01:36:43.430
Thirdly, you have to keep your eyes shut.

01:36:43.970 --> 01:36:45.770
You don't need not wear your spectacles.

01:36:45.870 --> 01:36:47.510
It has a better effect on your eyesight

01:36:47.510 --> 01:36:47.950
also.

01:36:48.410 --> 01:36:49.970
You don't have to open your eyes throughout.

01:36:57.750 --> 01:36:59.550
Fourthly, those who do not want to do,

01:36:59.810 --> 01:37:02.430
should go away, to be civil, to be

01:37:02.430 --> 01:37:03.190
kind to others.

01:37:17.150 --> 01:37:21.050
Because negative people disturb the happening, and the

01:37:21.050 --> 01:37:22.550
neighbors suffer from such people.

01:37:32.770 --> 01:37:35.996
It's a very sensitive and delicate happening, and

01:37:41.750 --> 01:37:43.190
it has to work out.

01:37:45.730 --> 01:37:47.750
The desire should be that it should work

01:37:47.750 --> 01:37:47.970
out.

01:37:52.190 --> 01:37:55.590
I cannot guarantee that hundred percent people will

01:37:55.590 --> 01:37:56.250
get it today.

01:37:57.750 --> 01:37:58.710
I cannot guarantee.

01:38:03.650 --> 01:38:05.270
But most of you should.

01:38:10.670 --> 01:38:12.430
Because you are quite complicated.

01:38:22.470 --> 01:38:24.490
So, simple things are to be done.

01:38:24.810 --> 01:38:27.010
First of all, we have to touch the

01:38:27.010 --> 01:38:27.510
Mother Earth.

01:38:27.670 --> 01:38:29.350
If you can take out your shoes, I'll

01:38:29.350 --> 01:38:29.750
be thankful.

01:38:44.310 --> 01:38:45.990
Little less could be better.

01:38:46.410 --> 01:38:48.330
Little less could be better.

01:38:48.610 --> 01:38:49.150
It's all right.

01:38:49.250 --> 01:38:49.650
It doesn't matter.

01:38:49.830 --> 01:38:51.710
For me, I'm quite used to them now.

01:38:58.610 --> 01:39:00.570
If you don't need them, better to put

01:39:00.570 --> 01:39:00.990
them off.

01:39:01.170 --> 01:39:02.730
For Me, it's too much sometimes, all the

01:39:02.730 --> 01:39:02.950
time.

01:39:05.230 --> 01:39:07.210
But the back ones are quite a lot

01:39:07.210 --> 01:39:07.710
also there.

01:39:07.950 --> 01:39:08.490
It's all right.

01:39:18.870 --> 01:39:21.730
Now, tomorrow I'll tell you that the left

01:39:21.730 --> 01:39:24.830
side in us is our emotional side, is

01:39:24.830 --> 01:39:27.390
the side of the heart, is the power

01:39:27.390 --> 01:39:28.170
of desire.

01:39:29.370 --> 01:39:32.210
And the Kundalini is the pure desire.

01:39:42.190 --> 01:39:45.110
And the right side is the power of

01:39:45.110 --> 01:39:45.450
action.

01:39:49.910 --> 01:39:52.510
Now, just to tell you, I'm telling you,

01:39:52.770 --> 01:39:55.130
but later on you will understand it fully

01:39:55.130 --> 01:39:55.990
what it is.

01:39:55.990 --> 01:39:58.170
It is not just like talking about something

01:39:58.170 --> 01:39:58.470
big.

01:39:58.650 --> 01:40:00.470
It's just you will know everything.

01:40:13.190 --> 01:40:15.570
Now, you have to put your left hand

01:40:15.570 --> 01:40:19.150
on your lap, very comfortably, very comfortably, on

01:40:19.150 --> 01:40:23.350
your lap, loudly.

01:40:24.970 --> 01:40:26.490
Loudly, they can't hear something.

01:40:32.810 --> 01:40:36.350
And the posture should be straight, need not

01:40:36.350 --> 01:40:39.130
bend, need not bend back, but straight, in

01:40:39.130 --> 01:40:39.810
a normal way.

01:40:50.110 --> 01:40:50.930
It's all right.

01:40:52.070 --> 01:40:52.750
This is better.

01:40:55.390 --> 01:40:58.930
Now, left hand towards Me, and right hand,

01:41:00.090 --> 01:41:01.570
first I'll tell you to put on your

01:41:01.570 --> 01:41:03.730
heart, because here resides the Spirit.

01:41:12.470 --> 01:41:14.570
Then the center, that is on the left

01:41:14.570 --> 01:41:15.870
-hand side of our stomach.

01:41:16.210 --> 01:41:17.550
The whole work we have to do on

01:41:17.550 --> 01:41:18.270
the left-hand side.

01:41:30.730 --> 01:41:33.890
Now, the left hand is, the left hand

01:41:33.890 --> 01:41:36.250
is always kept towards Me, like this.

01:41:36.710 --> 01:41:38.590
That is the desire that you want to

01:41:38.590 --> 01:41:39.630
get your Realization.

01:41:51.290 --> 01:41:54.710
Then the second center you have to touch

01:41:54.710 --> 01:41:57.890
with your right hand is on the left

01:41:57.890 --> 01:42:01.150
-hand side of your stomach, in the lower

01:42:01.150 --> 01:42:02.790
part of your abdomen.

01:42:15.470 --> 01:42:17.570
Now, again you have to raise them from

01:42:17.570 --> 01:42:20.370
there to the upper part of the stomach

01:42:20.370 --> 01:42:21.630
on the left-hand side.

01:42:32.770 --> 01:42:33.310
Little louder.

01:42:34.930 --> 01:42:37.170
And then again on your heart.

01:42:40.090 --> 01:42:41.470
You need not close your eyes first, you

01:42:41.470 --> 01:42:43.290
can see then I'll tell you what to

01:42:43.290 --> 01:42:43.490
say.

01:42:49.590 --> 01:42:52.630
Then this right hand on this center here,

01:42:52.710 --> 01:42:54.970
on the left-hand side, holding it tight.

01:43:02.290 --> 01:43:04.490
This is catching the worst among all of

01:43:04.490 --> 01:43:05.210
you.

01:43:10.330 --> 01:43:12.510
This center catches when we feel guilty.

01:43:16.530 --> 01:43:18.530
You should not feel guilty at all.

01:43:21.710 --> 01:43:23.490
As it is, you are the temple of

01:43:23.490 --> 01:43:23.770
God.

01:43:27.070 --> 01:43:29.150
There is no need to feel guilty at

01:43:29.150 --> 01:43:29.430
all.

01:43:29.570 --> 01:43:31.550
At the very outset I would request you

01:43:31.550 --> 01:43:32.530
not to feel guilty.

01:43:41.850 --> 01:43:44.690
Now, the right hand is taken on the

01:43:44.690 --> 01:43:45.850
forehead here.

01:43:49.610 --> 01:43:50.830
Now at the back.

01:43:54.090 --> 01:43:57.130
Then you have to stretch your hand and

01:43:57.130 --> 01:44:00.090
put this on the fontanel bone area here,

01:44:00.550 --> 01:44:02.030
where it was a soft bone.

01:44:13.470 --> 01:44:14.070
Loudly.

01:44:14.350 --> 01:44:15.410
And press it hard.

01:44:18.390 --> 01:44:19.930
Seven times you have to move it.

01:44:21.770 --> 01:44:22.390
That's all.

01:44:22.650 --> 01:44:26.110
Now we'll do it after closing our eyes.

01:44:26.530 --> 01:44:28.410
Only thing, remember, don't put your hand from

01:44:28.410 --> 01:44:30.110
this side, but when you come to this

01:44:30.110 --> 01:44:31.530
center you have to put it this way.

01:44:44.430 --> 01:44:44.970
All right.

01:44:46.130 --> 01:44:48.590
It's a very simple thing, anybody can do

01:44:48.590 --> 01:44:48.830
it.

01:44:49.530 --> 01:44:52.190
And you will be surprised that already so

01:44:52.190 --> 01:44:53.670
many of you have no thoughts in the

01:44:53.670 --> 01:44:53.890
mind.

01:44:54.090 --> 01:44:57.390
It's already crossed the Agnya, this portion, the

01:44:57.390 --> 01:44:58.670
center of Christ, it has crossed.

01:45:10.430 --> 01:45:11.350
I can see.

01:45:14.210 --> 01:45:17.330
Now, please put your left hand all the

01:45:17.330 --> 01:45:26.050
time towards Me and repeat in your heart

01:45:26.050 --> 01:45:26.810
what I say.

01:45:30.670 --> 01:45:34.430
First of all, first of all tell yourself

01:45:34.430 --> 01:45:36.270
that you are not guilty.

01:45:36.390 --> 01:45:39.090
I am not guilty, say that, in your

01:45:39.090 --> 01:45:39.310
heart.

01:45:44.050 --> 01:45:45.290
All right.

01:45:45.930 --> 01:45:47.270
Now close your eyes.

01:45:50.990 --> 01:45:53.670
Now put your right hand on your heart.

01:45:59.370 --> 01:46:01.450
Now you have to ask Me a question,

01:46:01.590 --> 01:46:03.690
you may call Me Shri Mataji or Mother,

01:46:03.870 --> 01:46:05.130
whichever way you like.

01:46:13.510 --> 01:46:17.890
You please ask Me a question, Mother, am

01:46:17.890 --> 01:46:18.650
I the Spirit?

01:46:27.700 --> 01:46:29.860
Close the eyes, close the eyes, don't keep

01:46:29.860 --> 01:46:30.220
them open.

01:46:30.320 --> 01:46:30.640
That's good.

01:46:31.660 --> 01:46:32.320
Close it.

01:46:32.520 --> 01:46:35.120
Because closing the eyes the attention is taken

01:46:35.120 --> 01:46:35.400
inside.

01:46:35.700 --> 01:46:37.060
Mother, am I the Spirit?

01:46:40.980 --> 01:46:41.740
Three times.

01:46:42.470 --> 01:46:44.780
I think you go nearer to the thing

01:46:44.780 --> 01:46:46.080
because they can't hear you.

01:46:55.420 --> 01:46:59.300
Now this question follows another question, that if

01:46:59.300 --> 01:47:01.700
you are the Spirit, you are your own

01:47:01.700 --> 01:47:06.060
guide, your own guru, you are your own

01:47:06.060 --> 01:47:06.440
master.

01:47:14.960 --> 01:47:17.560
So now you put your right hand on

01:47:17.560 --> 01:47:19.420
the upper part of your stomach, on the

01:47:19.420 --> 01:47:22.200
left hand side, which is the center of

01:47:22.200 --> 01:47:22.840
mastery.

01:47:38.560 --> 01:47:42.120
This is the center which is created by

01:47:42.120 --> 01:47:45.800
the masters, the great masters who are Sadhgurus,

01:47:45.860 --> 01:47:47.640
who are real masters.

01:47:55.580 --> 01:48:01.140
Like Abraham, Moses, Janak, Nanak.

01:48:06.500 --> 01:48:09.480
Lao Tse, Mohammad Sahab.

01:48:16.400 --> 01:48:23.280
Now you take this hand, little deep, prayers,

01:48:24.600 --> 01:48:27.780
push it little deep into that area in

01:48:27.780 --> 01:48:30.740
the upper part of the abdomen and ask

01:48:30.740 --> 01:48:34.360
a question three times, Mother, am I my

01:48:34.360 --> 01:48:35.120
own guide?

01:48:35.680 --> 01:48:37.240
Am I my own master?

01:48:37.780 --> 01:48:39.200
Am I my own guru?

01:48:39.980 --> 01:48:41.280
Ask in your heart.

01:48:45.620 --> 01:48:48.420
Ask a question.

01:48:58.260 --> 01:49:03.360
In your heart.

01:49:09.480 --> 01:49:11.540
This will neutralize if you have been to

01:49:11.540 --> 01:49:12.840
some wrong master.

01:49:32.196 --> 01:49:33.769
Please be seated Sir

01:49:38.466 --> 01:49:39.873
Sıcaklamış olmalısınız

01:50:03.456 --> 01:50:07.170
Now, don't pay attention to others, it's a

01:50:07.170 --> 01:50:09.190
time for you to pay attention to yourself.

01:50:14.490 --> 01:50:16.130
When are you going to pay attention to

01:50:16.130 --> 01:50:16.590
yourself?

01:50:19.350 --> 01:50:20.710
Loudly, why do you go down?

01:50:26.770 --> 01:50:28.970
Now, now this hand is to be taken

01:50:28.970 --> 01:50:31.810
down below on the lower part of the

01:50:31.810 --> 01:50:34.996
abdomen, on the left hand side please,

01:50:43.830 --> 01:50:50.930
lower part, loudly just say, press

01:50:50.930 --> 01:50:51.330
it hard.

01:50:53.570 --> 01:50:57.910
This is the center which gives you the

01:50:57.910 --> 01:51:01.730
true knowledge or works out the technique of

01:51:01.730 --> 01:51:03.136
true knowledge

01:51:11.390 --> 01:51:17.530
called as Shuddha Vidya, that's the technique of

01:51:17.530 --> 01:51:19.210
working out God's laws.

01:51:25.350 --> 01:51:29.730
So to awaken this, I have to ask

01:51:29.730 --> 01:51:33.070
you that I cannot cross your freedom.

01:51:41.890 --> 01:51:45.510
You have to ask, Mother please give me

01:51:45.510 --> 01:51:46.530
true knowledge.

01:51:54.070 --> 01:51:56.810
Please ask six times because this center has

01:51:56.810 --> 01:51:57.710
got six petals.

01:52:05.950 --> 01:52:07.950
Can you get me some water, it's too

01:52:07.950 --> 01:52:08.370
hot.

01:52:11.010 --> 01:52:13.590
Right, right Agnya, it's too much.

01:52:27.420 --> 01:52:29.120
Please ask six times.

01:52:43.099 --> 01:52:45.530
Right Agnya, it's too much.

01:52:50.100 --> 01:52:51.500
Now better, better.

01:52:55.896 --> 01:52:56.779
Now

01:52:59.586 --> 01:53:01.786
now by asking this

01:53:02.700 --> 01:53:04.655
The Kundalini starts

01:53:04.680 --> 01:53:05.513
moving.

01:53:10.340 --> 01:53:16.540
Raise your right hand on the upper part

01:53:16.540 --> 01:53:18.960
of your abdomen on the left hand side

01:53:18.960 --> 01:53:21.860
and again push it with your fingers.

01:53:25.710 --> 01:53:28.070
Raise right hand on the upper part of

01:53:28.070 --> 01:53:28.530
the abdomen.

01:53:38.480 --> 01:53:41.200
Now as the Kundalini is awakening you have

01:53:41.200 --> 01:53:43.800
to give a seat to the Kundalini or

01:53:43.800 --> 01:53:45.720
the assurance to the Kundalini.

01:53:52.920 --> 01:53:59.060
Without feeling guilty, with full confidence in yourself,

01:54:06.353 --> 01:54:10.100
you assert by saying, Mother

01:54:10.100 --> 01:54:14.000
I am my own guru, I am my

01:54:14.000 --> 01:54:17.900
own master, I am my own guide, ten

01:54:17.900 --> 01:54:20.300
times because there are ten gurus.

01:54:33.510 --> 01:54:36.650
Ten times, with full confidence in you.

01:54:55.800 --> 01:54:59.840
Now, ten times it is to be said,

01:55:00.520 --> 01:55:01.960
with full confidence.

01:55:22.040 --> 01:55:26.520
Now raise this right hand again on to

01:55:26.520 --> 01:55:28.840
the heart where resides your spirit.

01:55:34.913 --> 01:55:37.480
This center has got twelve petals.

01:55:43.460 --> 01:55:56.660
So please say twelve times, full assertion, full

01:55:56.660 --> 01:55:57.940
confidence in yourself.

01:56:00.780 --> 01:56:03.940
Mother, I am the spirit.

01:56:07.300 --> 01:56:13.320
Say it twelve times, with full confidence.

01:56:15.440 --> 01:56:17.460
Mother, I am the spirit.

01:56:49.973 --> 01:56:55.080
You must know that the Divine is not

01:56:55.080 --> 01:57:00.860
only the ocean of love and compassion but

01:57:00.860 --> 01:57:03.840
it is the ocean of forgiveness.

01:57:16.960 --> 01:57:20.420
So you please don't have any guilt in

01:57:20.420 --> 01:57:20.940
your mind.

01:57:21.780 --> 01:57:24.480
Forgive yourself first of all.

01:57:32.020 --> 01:57:38.620
Raise this hand in the corner of the

01:57:38.620 --> 01:57:45.580
base of the neck and your shoulder

01:57:46.843 --> 01:57:50.290
And at this center you must say with full

01:57:50.290 --> 01:57:54.790
confidence, Mother I am not guilty, sixteen times.

01:58:07.230 --> 01:58:08.530
Sixteen times.

01:58:12.910 --> 01:58:15.470
Put the left hand towards Me and the

01:58:15.470 --> 01:58:25.310
right hand, put it on the lap,

01:58:25.550 --> 01:58:26.710
parallel to the lap.

01:58:26.970 --> 01:58:29.050
Better, it's better.

01:58:30.790 --> 01:58:32.150
Please don't feel guilty.

01:58:41.760 --> 01:58:43.080
Ah, it's rising.

01:58:59.240 --> 01:59:03.340
Now raise this right hand on your forehead

01:59:03.340 --> 01:59:06.080
across and press it on both the sides.

01:59:14.880 --> 01:59:16.640
Press it on both the sides.

01:59:20.360 --> 01:59:26.300
Now here you say from your heart, how

01:59:26.300 --> 01:59:27.980
many times is not the point, from your

01:59:27.980 --> 01:59:31.700
heart, Mother I forgive everyone.

01:59:41.680 --> 01:59:49.340
You may think, now you may think that

01:59:49.340 --> 01:59:56.400
it is difficult to forgive but if you

01:59:56.400 --> 01:59:58.500
do not forgive or you forgive it is

01:59:58.500 --> 01:59:58.880
a myth.

02:00:04.020 --> 02:00:06.900
But when you forgive you do not play

02:00:06.900 --> 02:00:08.280
into the hands of others.

02:00:14.620 --> 02:00:16.740
So from your heart just say, Mother I

02:00:16.740 --> 02:00:19.240
forgive, you feel very much relieved, I forgive

02:00:19.240 --> 02:00:19.680
everyone.

02:00:28.180 --> 02:00:31.700
Now to get over your guilt you put

02:00:31.700 --> 02:00:33.820
your right hand on the back side of

02:00:33.820 --> 02:00:35.740
your head, just to get over your guilt,

02:00:35.860 --> 02:00:36.940
don't feel guilty.

02:00:45.700 --> 02:00:48.780
I only say that if I have done

02:00:48.780 --> 02:00:52.540
any mistakes, in the glory of the Divine,

02:00:52.900 --> 02:00:53.820
please forgive Me.

02:01:05.393 --> 02:01:08.260
But don't feel guilty

02:01:15.423 --> 02:01:16.543
it's better.

02:01:18.046 --> 02:01:19.022
Now

02:01:19.980 --> 02:01:23.180
Now raise your right hand on top of

02:01:23.180 --> 02:01:31.820
your head, stretch your fingers and put your

02:01:31.820 --> 02:01:35.740
palm on the fontanel bone area and try

02:01:35.740 --> 02:01:37.940
to press it hard and move it seven

02:01:37.940 --> 02:01:38.580
times.

02:01:48.020 --> 02:01:50.080
Press it hard.

02:01:52.240 --> 02:01:56.080
Now here again I cannot cross your freedom,

02:02:01.680 --> 02:02:04.160
so you have to ask for your Self

02:02:04.160 --> 02:02:08.500
Realization seven times saying, Mother please may I

02:02:08.500 --> 02:02:10.760
have the Self Realization I want it.

02:02:27.600 --> 02:02:30.740
Heart, stretch it

02:02:50.939 --> 02:02:51.940
Seven times.

02:03:33.540 --> 02:03:37.080
Now take down your right hand slowly on

02:03:37.080 --> 02:03:37.540
your lap.

02:03:47.360 --> 02:03:49.540
Please slowly open your eyes.

02:03:55.360 --> 02:03:58.640
Without thinking you are mostly in thoughtless awareness,

02:03:58.780 --> 02:04:00.400
most of you.

02:04:05.540 --> 02:04:08.080
You can feel on top of your head

02:04:08.080 --> 02:04:08.760
the cool breeze.

02:04:08.760 --> 02:04:11.000
Now with the left hand, put the right

02:04:11.000 --> 02:04:13.500
hand towards Me and with the left hand,

02:04:26.706 --> 02:04:28.860
see if there's a cool breeze coming.

02:04:28.980 --> 02:04:29.900
Please open your eyes.

02:04:36.160 --> 02:04:37.660
You may open your eyes.

02:04:40.920 --> 02:04:43.080
On the fontanel bone area, it's little in

02:04:43.080 --> 02:04:43.700
the front side.

02:04:49.660 --> 02:04:50.920
It is a subtle thing.

02:04:53.900 --> 02:04:57.640
For some people feel the heat.

02:05:06.190 --> 02:05:07.530
Are you feeling?

02:05:08.986 --> 02:05:09.919
Good

02:05:13.020 --> 02:05:15.460
Now take your right hand and see, left

02:05:15.460 --> 02:05:16.180
hand towards Me.

02:05:21.760 --> 02:05:23.800
Keep your eyes open.

02:05:27.260 --> 02:05:28.460
See it without thinking.

02:05:34.520 --> 02:05:36.620
You are a seeker, that's the main point,

02:05:36.760 --> 02:05:37.460
must know that.

02:05:37.820 --> 02:05:39.280
That's the most important point.

02:05:40.020 --> 02:05:41.160
The rest of it you forget.

02:05:42.100 --> 02:05:44.400
Now put the right hand again.

02:05:47.300 --> 02:05:48.340
See with the left hand.

02:05:50.880 --> 02:05:51.840
It's very subtle.

02:05:56.690 --> 02:05:58.410
See are you feeling the cool breeze?

02:06:03.503 --> 02:06:06.296
Another hand , yes. Good, good

02:06:09.283 --> 02:06:11.430
You can put your hands up there and

02:06:11.430 --> 02:06:12.210
ask a question.

02:06:12.843 --> 02:06:15.250
Up there, put your heads up

02:06:18.250 --> 02:06:21.850
And ask a question, Mother, is this the cool breeze

02:06:21.850 --> 02:06:22.870
of the Holy Ghost?

02:06:23.530 --> 02:06:25.090
Cool breeze of the Adi Shakti?

02:06:25.510 --> 02:06:27.810
Is this the all-pervading power of God's

02:06:27.810 --> 02:06:27.990
love?

02:06:41.310 --> 02:06:44.643
Is this the all-pervading power of God's love

02:06:49.050 --> 02:06:50.650
Now put down your hands.

02:06:51.610 --> 02:06:52.770
Now see on your hands.

02:06:54.730 --> 02:06:56.130
See on your hands.

02:06:57.630 --> 02:06:59.070
Feeling it in your hands also.

02:07:02.310 --> 02:07:04.870
This is the power that is called as

02:07:04.870 --> 02:07:05.870
Ritambhara Prajna.

02:07:11.150 --> 02:07:14.996
This is the power that does all living work

02:07:19.370 --> 02:07:21.156
Just feel it, it's in the hand

02:07:21.181 --> 02:07:22.030
You can feel it.

02:07:25.143 --> 02:07:27.270
It's there, it's there.

02:07:27.890 --> 02:07:29.730
Now for the first time you are feeling

02:07:29.730 --> 02:07:30.490
this power.

02:07:37.410 --> 02:07:39.570
That is what actualization.

02:07:43.610 --> 02:07:45.230
It's not just lecture.

02:07:49.110 --> 02:07:50.930
You are beyond thoughts.

02:07:51.090 --> 02:07:52.790
You see yourself, there's no thought in your

02:07:52.790 --> 02:07:53.910
mind, in silence.

02:08:00.250 --> 02:08:02.410
Some have not felt it, does not matter.

02:08:06.390 --> 02:08:08.890
Again day after tomorrow, I'll tell you what

02:08:08.890 --> 02:08:09.630
is the Spirit.

02:08:16.330 --> 02:08:19.750
Now go home and do not talk, because

02:08:19.750 --> 02:08:21.910
you will again go into the level of

02:08:21.910 --> 02:08:22.290
thinking.

02:08:29.096 --> 02:08:30.170
Just relax.

02:08:33.370 --> 02:08:36.310
Hope to see you day after tomorrow again.

02:08:40.890 --> 02:08:44.090
Also bring your questions, if you are left

02:08:44.090 --> 02:08:44.590
with any.

02:08:47.330 --> 02:08:48.150
Did you feel?

02:08:49.550 --> 02:08:49.790
No?

02:08:51.990 --> 02:08:53.750
Some have not felt it, I know, but

02:08:53.750 --> 02:08:55.150
it's all right, we'll work it out.

02:09:01.450 --> 02:09:04.750
But do not waste time in questioning, but

02:09:04.750 --> 02:09:06.990
in getting realization is important.

02:09:15.910 --> 02:09:18.190
Because you are seekers of ages.

02:09:22.610 --> 02:09:24.550
And don't waste this life.

02:09:28.490 --> 02:09:31.250
Nothing is more important than your Spirit.

02:09:35.030 --> 02:09:36.330
May God bless you all.

02:09:38.770 --> 02:09:41.130
I'll meet you again day after tomorrow.

02:09:41.130 --> 02:09:45.510
Please bring all your friends, all those whom

02:09:45.510 --> 02:09:46.930
you know as seekers.

02:09:47.210 --> 02:09:49.070
This is the greatest thing you can give

02:09:49.070 --> 02:09:49.830
to your friends.

02:10:01.170 --> 02:10:03.310
This is the last judgment.

02:10:07.590 --> 02:10:10.270
You are judged by yourself.

02:10:12.730 --> 02:10:14.010
May God bless you.

02:10:55.110 --> 02:10:55.950
Thank you.

02:10:57.970 --> 02:10:58.950
How are you?

02:10:59.330 --> 02:10:59.850
All right?

02:11:00.770 --> 02:11:01.730
Thank you very much.

02:11:24.010 --> 02:11:25.150
Thank you very much.